          "**Intellectual** — strategy, deception, outwitting",
          "**Emotional** — manipulation, betrayal, intimacy weaponized",
          "**Moral** — forcing impossible choices; making the protagonist complicit",
          "**Thematic** — embodying the counter-argument to the protagonist's worldview"
        ]
      },
      "uniqueItems": true,
      "description": "Multi-select checkbox group",
